  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a kadhai over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and saute until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the annatto seeds and cook, stirring constantly, for 1 minute.",
    "Add the flaked smoked mackerel, fish sauce, vinegar, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the rendered pork fat and stir until melted and combined.",
    "Add the mustard and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, stirring occasionally, for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped green onions if desired."
